    <body>
    
        <h1>Travel to ....</h1>
        <p> find perfect place for yourself</p>
        <h2>Japan</h2>
        <img src="https://cdn.kastatic.org/third_party/javascript-khansrc/live-editor/build/images/landscapes/mountains-and-lake.png" width="350" alt="Japan landscape">
        <p class="description">With a population of over 123 million as of 2025, it is the world's 11th most populous country. Tokyo is the country's capital and largest city.</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Walk around Tokyo (Shibuya Crossing, Harajuku)</li>
            <li>Explore Kyoto temples and shrines</li>
            <li>Visit Osaka street food markets</li>
            <li>Ride the Shinkansen (bullet train)</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Hawaiʻi</h2>
        <img src="https://cdn.kastatic.org/third_party/javascript-khansrc/live-editor/build/images/landscapes/beach-in-hawaii.png" width="350" alt="Hawaiʻi beach">
        <p class="description">Hawaii is an island state of the United States, in the Pacific Ocean about 2,000 miles (3,200 km) southwest of the U.S. mainland</p>
        
        <ul>
            <li>Go surfing</li>
            <li>Hike Diamond Head volcano</li>
            <li>Attend a luau (Hawaiian feast & dance show)</li>
            <li>Learn hula dancing</li>
        </ul>
        
        <h2>Switzerland</h2>
        <img src="https://cdn.kastatic.org/third_party/javascript-khansrc/live-editor/build/images/landscapes/mountain_matterhorn.png" width="350" alt="mountains">
        <p class="description">Switzerland, officially the Swiss Confederation, is a landlocked country located at the intersection of Central, Western, and Southern Europe.</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Ride cable cars in the Swiss Alps</li>
            <li>Ski or snowboard in winter</li>
            <li>Walk around Zurich old town</li>
            <li>Visit waterfalls in Lauterbrunnen</li>
        </ul>
